snippet.title: Beat the Wall (Miniclip Flash Game)
snippet.description:
Me playing this excellent game of kick out. Great 3D graphics and good ball effects, but hard to score!
*2020 UPDATE NEW FULL OST VIDEO*
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sAYM9VVo6CA

The link of the game was:

http://www.miniclip.com/games/beat-the-wall/en/

+1.2M channel views and only ~400 subscribers, please remember to like and subscribe, also I would really appreciate a follow on my Twitch:

http://www.twitch.tv/SirRocafort 

Thank you very much!!
